2011-09-08T09:09:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/epistar-corp-august-sales-fall-27-80-table-2448-tt.html
EPISTAR CORP (2448)  said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 27.80% to NT$1,397,030,000 from NT$1,935,027,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales           1,397,030        1,935,027   
YOY%             -27.80%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           12,635,335       13,111,583  
YOY%              -3.63% 
=================================================================
 